{"tid":1124287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵加價3.3%推遲4個月生效「通車40周年與市民分享成果」","createTime":"2019-04-25T02:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T03:39:10.000Z","uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d02ba82ea634b5715e79f0b5589eb744d1df18b3","tid":1124287,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"港鐵上月根據票價調整機制，於6月起可加價3.3%，港鐵昨日（24日）宣布，每程97折優惠（實際扣減3.3%）將由原定6個月延長至10個月，即至2020年4月初，意味港鐵至明年4月實際上也未加價。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵與政府商討後，考慮到今年是港鐵通車40周年，為與市民分享成果，決定再以額外資源，延長提供每程3.3%的扣減優惠，至合共40個星期，優惠金額逾4億元，每位八達通乘客的實際車費由2019年6月至2020年4月初將不會上調；而「港鐵都會票」、「全月通加強版」及「屯門&mdash;&mdash;南昌全日通」亦會維持現行售價，同樣至2020年4月初。(節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2335219/港鐵加價3.3-推遲4個月生效%E3%80%80稱「通車40周年與市民分享成果」?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2335219%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B93.3-%E6%8E%A8%E9%81%B24%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88%25E3%2580%2580%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A40%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E8%88%87%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%8D%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SSTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=48f97999\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2335219/港鐵加價3.3-推遲4個月生效%E3%80%80稱「通車40周年與市民分享成果」?mtc=20023</a></span>"},{"pid":"010306f19f4ba954d1191dc83b3c06696b4d0cae","tid":1124287,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25521acfffe77bb5a880d587d4c3c157cd97f69f","tid":1124287,"uid":22422,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"謝主隆恩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會撞多四次車贈慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" c